; Name ..........: _GUI_STATE
; Description ...: This file Includes several files in the current script and all Declared variables, constant, or create an array.
; Syntax ........: #include , Global
; Parameters ....: $action_groupe, $group_de_controle
; Return values .: None
; Author ........: Boju(06-2016)
